                                <condition>The ogham inscription is well-preserved for the most part except for a potentially substantial portion missing from the beginning. The end of the inscription, however, appears to be complete despite the fracture at the upper edge of the slab. The two broad faces are severely laminated and large chunks of the surface have been lost. </condition>
